doing business with a young director.

258
00:17:37,590 --> 00:17:39,000
No calls, please.

259
00:17:39,090 --> 00:17:40,090
Come on.

260
00:17:41,210 --> 00:17:43,460
Funny, you were the receptionist before.

261
00:17:43,540 --> 00:17:44,750
Yes.

262
00:17:45,090 --> 00:17:47,470
