like a microwave.

363
00:23:00,440 --> 00:23:02,560
We'll dub it in post.

364
00:23:04,480 --> 00:23:05,350
[Knock on door]
Okay.

365
00:23:05,440 --> 00:23:06,350
Yes?

366
00:23:06,440 --> 00:23:09,190
