374
00:23:31,310 --> 00:23:35,310
You couldn't make me happier.
I've been working on this for years.

375
00:23:36,270 --> 00:23:38,270
Can we go back to the pain?

376
00:23:38,970 --> 00:23:42,550
 How do we see the pain
