379
00:23:49,310 --> 00:23:50,900
How do they groan?

380
00:23:51,550 --> 00:23:53,300
They groan, I think, with pain.

381
00:23:53,390 --> 00:23:55,190
I'm not sure what you mean.

382
00:24:07,390 --> 00:24:08,770
