00:34:04,990 --> 00:34:07,900
Yes. On the inside
of your head.

485
00:34:09,160 --> 00:34:10,330
What does that mean?

486
00:34:10,410 --> 00:34:12,750
Well, it means a lot
of unpleasant things

487
00:34:12,820 --> 00:34:15,360
